  <h3>Shared Contraindications</h3>
  <p style="font-size:14px;margin-bottom:0;">Both medications carry warnings for: personal or family history of medullary thyroid carcinoma (MTC), multiple endocrine neoplasia syndrome type 2 (MEN2), history of <a href="/articles/peptide-side-effects-what-to-know">pancreatitis</a>, pregnancy or planned pregnancy, and severe gastrointestinal disease. These are not lifestyle drugs. They require medical supervision and monitoring.</p>
</div>

<!-- ========== DOSING ========== -->
